pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Prebiotic Gut Goodness 75g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With inulin derived from organic Jerusalem
Artichoke and resistant starch derived from organic
Green Banana as natural sources of prebiotic fibre.

Wanderlust Prebiotic Gut Goodness is a consciously created plant-active fibre blend. With inulin derived from organic Jerusalem Artichoke and resistant starch derived from organic Green Banana as natural sources of prebiotic fibre. Additional wholefood powders provide a natural source of fibre to help keep your gut happy by maintaining bowel regularity.

Size: 75 g NET

Ingredients

INGREDINETS: Inulin derived from Jerusalem Artichoke* (37.5%), Green Banana
Resistant Starch*(21.5%), Boabab Powder*, Pear Powder, Chia Seed Powder*, Green Kiwi Fruit Powder, Australian Desert Lime Powder.

*Organic ingredients.

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

SERVING SUGGESTION: Mix 4 g (1 ½ teaspoons) of powder into water, juice,
milk of choice, your favourite smoothie or breakfast bowl.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat and sunlight. Do not use if inner seal is missing or broken.
